headline: Regency Centers Boosts Portfolio With Nashville Property Acquisition
summary: In a bid to expand its portfolio, REG acquires a premier retail destination in the high-growth market of Nashville.

headline: How Open Text, Regency Centers, And Delek Logistics Can Put Cash In Your Pocket
summary: Companies with a long history of paying dividends and consistently hiking them remain appealing to income-focused investors.
